item.title: California Canvass Map
item.description: I’ll likely be revisiting this project in the future to see how my analysis has changed. With that said, I’m presenting this project as I did in 2016. So much has changed in the last four years. I’m excited to rework this project and pull in some fresh data. It should make for a very interesting before-and-after. Final product, top left, with the three layers used for analysis and composition {% include gallery id=“gallery” caption=“Paper Map Examples at Regional, District and City Levels” %}
